{"article_id":"EyFPNp1R9tLAxj1q","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The House Judiciary Committee on Thursday approved a resolution","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"defining the rules of the panel 's impeachment investigation , the first vote","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"the committee has taken","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"related to the potential impeachment of President Donald Trump .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"The party-line vote came","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"as House Democrats have struggled to define the committee 's probe ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"with Judiciary Chairman Jerry Nadler saying","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"the committee is conducting an impeachment inquiry ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"while House Speaker Nancy Pelosi and other Democratic leaders are refraining from calling it that .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Thursday 's vote ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"which does not need to be approved by the full House ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"gives Nadler the ability","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"to deem committee hearings as impeachment hearings .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"It allows staff to question witnesses at those hearings for an hour","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"after members conclude ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"gives the President 's lawyers the ability","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to respond in writing to public testimony","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and allows the committee to collect information in a closed setting .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"But the dissonant messages over the probe have prompted frustration among rank-and-file members , particularly those in competitive races wary of impeachment ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"and it even led to the House 's No . 2 Democrat walking back his statement on the committee 's investigation on Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"At her weekly news conference Thursday , Pelosi once again declined to say","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"the committee was conducting an impeachment investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"which happened","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"minutes after the committee adopted its resolution","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"stating","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"that 's what it was in fact doing .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Nadler sought to clarify the committee 's intentions in his opening statement at Thursday 's committee meeting ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"acknowledging","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"there was confusion","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"but arguing","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"that the language","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"used to describe the investigation","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"was n't the important point .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"`` This Committee is engaged in an investigation","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"that will allow us to determine","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"whether to recommend articles of impeachment with respect to President Trump .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Some call this process an impeachment inquiry .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Some call it an impeachment investigation .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"There is no legal difference between these terms ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"and I no longer care to argue about the nomenclature , ''","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"the New York Democrat said .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"`` But let me clear up any remaining doubt :","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"The conduct under investigation poses a threat to our democracy .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"We have an obligation","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"to respond to this threat .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"And we are doing so . ''","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"But Georgia Rep. Doug Collins , the top Republican on the Judiciary Committee , charged","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that the committee had become `` a giant Instagram filter '' -","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that Democrats were trying to dress up what they were really doing","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"to make it look better .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"He argued","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"that the Democratic resolution was `` not anything special ''","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"because it grants the chairman powers","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that he already has access to .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"`` The difference between formal impeachment proceedings and what we 're doing today is a world apart","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"no matter what the chairman just said , ''","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Collins said ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"adding later ,","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` The chairman can do this at any time ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"because he wants the appearance of something","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"that it 's not .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"You 're not in an impeachment inquiry . ''","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"After the committee vote , Collins accused Democrats of `` trying to cover '' for their moderate members","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"by not voting in the full House","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"to formally establish an impeachment inquiry .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"The committee 's new procedures for its hearings could be on display as soon as next week ,","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"when former Trump campaign manager Corey Lewandowski is scheduled to appear on Tuesday .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"The committee in July subpoenaed Lewandowski and former White House aides Rick Dearborn and Rob Porter to testify on Tuesday ,","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"but it 's not clear if the White House will direct Dearborn and Porter not to appear ,","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"making the same immunity claims","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"it has with former White House counsel Don McGahn and others .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Nadler vowed an `` aggressive series of hearings '' under the committee 's procedures","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"approved on Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"`` The investigation will go well beyond the four corners of the Mueller report ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"and we will be starting with a first hearing on September 17th ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"we expect among others , we expect Mr. Lewandowski to testify , ''","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Nadler and committee members say","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"that adopting the resolution will make their investigation more effective","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"as they gather information","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"-- through subpoenas , hearings and the courts --","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"to decide whether to introduce articles of impeachment against the President .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"But the broader question","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"-- is the committee conducting an impeachment inquiry ? --","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"has flustered Democrats all week .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"To Nadler and many on the committee , the committee is conducting an impeachment investigation .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"They argue","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that the debate over how to label the investigation","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"is merely semantics :","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"they have stated publicly and in court filings","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"that their investigation is part of an active effort","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"to decide","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"whether to pursue impeachment .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"House leadership , however , has taken a different tack .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Pelosi and Majority Leader Steny Hoyer have declined this week to say affirmatively","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"that the committee 's investigation was an impeachment investigation or an impeachment inquiry ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"as Nadler has described it .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"`` I stand by what he have been doing all along .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"I support what is happening in the Judiciary Committee","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"that enables them to do their process of interrogation and their investigation ,","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"and I salute them for that work , ''","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"Pelosi said","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"when asked","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"if the committee was conducting an impeachment investigation .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"When reporters pressed her","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"if she was uncomfortable with the term `` impeachment inquiry , ''","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"which was embraced by many Democrats ,","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"Pelosi turned to the Senate instead .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"`` Why do n't we spend some time","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"going over to see Mitch McConnell","depth":17},{"id":111,"text":"and asking him","depth":18},{"id":112,"text":"why he does n't want to save lives ? ''","depth":18},{"id":113,"text":"she asked reporters ,","depth":16},{"id":114,"text":"referring to Democratic efforts","depth":17},{"id":115,"text":"to advance House-passed background checks legislation in the Senate .","depth":17},{"id":116,"text":"`` Why is it that you 're hung up on a word over here ,","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"when lives are at stake over there ? ''","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"Hoyer responded `` no '' on Wednesday","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"when asked","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"whether the House was in an impeachment inquiry .","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"But later that day , he issued a statement","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"clarifying his comments .","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"`` I thought","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"the question was in regards to whether the full House is actively considering articles of impeachment ,","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"which we are not at this time , ''","depth":16},{"id":126,"text":"Hoyer said .","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"`` I strongly support Chairman Nadler and the Judiciary Committee Democrats","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"as they proceed with their investigation","depth":16},{"id":129,"text":"'to determine whether to recommend articles of impeachment to the full House , '","depth":17},{"id":130,"text":"as the resolution states .","depth":17},{"id":131,"text":"It is critical that Congress have access to all of the relevant facts ,","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"and we will follow those facts","depth":16},{"id":133,"text":"wherever they lead ,","depth":17},{"id":134,"text":"including impeachment . ''","depth":17},{"id":135,"text":"Hoyer 's statement , however , refrained from referencing an impeachment inquiry or investigation .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"Asked by CNN Wednesday evening","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"whether he believed","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"the committee was conducting an impeachment investigation ,","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"he declined to say :","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"`` You saw my statement","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"-- I 'm not going to say anything else . ''","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"And House Caucus Chairman Hakeem Jeffries ,","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"who is a Judiciary Committee member ,","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"said Wednesday","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"he did n't `` want to get caught in semantics ''","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"when asked","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"if the committee 's probe was an impeachment inquiry .","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"Following Thursday 's vote on the committee resolution ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"Jeffries told CNN","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"that the committee was `` conducting an impeachment investigation into the culture of corruption , abuse of power and obstruction of justice . ''","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"Rep. Jamie Raskin , a Maryland Democrat on the Judiciary Committee","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"who has called the probe an impeachment inquiry ,","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"the dispute is emblematic of broader divisions","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"about what to do about impeachment .","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"Is it wise to pursue ,","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"he said","depth":15},{"id":158,"text":"some have suggested ,","depth":15},{"id":159,"text":"when the House knows","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"the Senate wo n't act ?","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"`` There are 100 views out there about the right way","depth":15},{"id":162,"text":"of dealing with the President ,","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"even among people","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"who agree","depth":16},{"id":165,"text":"he 's committed high crimes and misdemeanors , ''","depth":16},{"id":166,"text":"Raskin said .","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"`` If you believe","depth":15},{"id":168,"text":"that we are not of one mind about how to proceed ,","depth":15},{"id":169,"text":"you 're absolutely right .","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"Nobody knows exactly , ultimately about how to proceed .","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"But everybody believes","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"we can not let the President get away with corruption and malpractice in office . ''","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"While Democrats have suggested","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"the dispute","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"over labeling the panel 's investigation is n't important as the work itself ,","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"the question","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"of whether the committee is conducting an impeachment inquiry","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"could have implications","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"when the Judiciary Committee 's lawsuits go before a judge in the coming weeks .","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"The committee is suing","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"to obtain former special counsel Robert Mueller 's grand jury material","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"and to force McGahn to testify ,","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"and it has argued in court filings","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"its investigation is part of an active consideration","depth":14},{"id":185,"text":"of whether to impeach the President .","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"`` It 's the facts","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"that we need to see , ''","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"said Rep. Steve Cohen , a Tennessee Democrat","depth":14},{"id":189,"text":"who has pushed for Trump 's impeachment .","depth":14},{"id":190,"text":"`` Proof needs to come out ,","depth":15},{"id":191,"text":"and what they call it makes no difference to me","depth":16},{"id":192,"text":"and I do n't know","depth":17},{"id":193,"text":"what it 's called .","depth":17},{"id":194,"text":"But this will be an investigation for impeachment .","depth":15},{"id":195,"text":"There is no question about it .","depth":15},{"id":196,"text":"People are stumbling over it","depth":16},{"id":197,"text":"because of politics ,","depth":16},{"id":198,"text":"so be it .","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"It 's the facts","depth":15},{"id":200,"text":"that need to be introduced to the American people","depth":16},{"id":201,"text":"to hear for the most impeachable President in the history of this country . ''","depth":16}],"relations":[{"parent":403,"left":0,"right":402,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":402,"left":266,"right":401,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":219,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":210,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":205,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":1,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":203,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":5,"right":208,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":6,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{